{"tid":2119292,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"公院瀕爆煲 非緊急手術延期","createTime":"2020-07-22T04:26:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-22T04:32:05.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"95fc4b39051d1a96650f684eb0169a75c2b31f57","tid":2119292,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T04:26:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200722/Q3JY3UFUYRRJVOQ42L6Y4Q7W3U/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200722%2FQ3JY3UFUYRRJVOQ42L6Y4Q7W3U%2F&d=ubUSuZPfwFYlyx9%2FldNtB7JtyMJyNHaGyUrVEdcKl1A%3D&h=983a4f08\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200722%2FQ3JY3UFUYRRJVOQ42L6Y4Q7W3U%2F&h=26eab82b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200722/Q3JY3UFUYRRJVOQ42L6Y4Q7W3U/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n公院瀕爆煲 非緊急手術延期<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】不斷擴張的武漢肺炎疫潮沒有停竭迹象，公立醫療系統瀕臨崩潰。醫管局總行政經理張子峯出席港台節目《千禧年代》時表示，現時已使用約77%病床。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：入境免檢疫種禍 口罩令太遲<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/VoxtGITO5CEiMWlna4LTi4MT_XY=/640x426/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/NCG33E3J725NU4IMOINPUUKZ3Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FVoxtGITO5CEiMWlna4LTi4MT_XY%3D%2F640x426%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FNCG33E3J725NU4IMOINPUUKZ3Q.jpg&h=a76e8088&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n張子峯<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n衞署多項服務暫停<br />\n<br />\n由於要預留一定病床處理急症等情況，當使用量到達八成多已屬很滿，加上有長者及長期病患入院，有時要用深切治療服務，部份。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n衞生署亦公佈，轄下部份非緊急服務已作調整或暫停。受影響的服務包括母嬰健康院、兒童體能智力測驗服務、學生健康服務中心、。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n署方轄下的牙科診所，包括政府牙科診所，學童牙科診所及口腔頜面外科及牙科診所只限提供緊急及止痛服務，其中口腔頜面外科及牙科診所將會繼續。。。。。。。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"add0caa73ec7190c351f421354d0978927daca9f","tid":2119292,"uid":122134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T04:32:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}